{"tid":1537100,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武請入","createTime":"2019-09-03T20:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T23:00:58.000Z","uid":45844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d37615d013fb17d1db470afbe4d26b399fb1a0bc","tid":1537100,"uid":45844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:50:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pqzKQnmq0Cs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpqzKQnmq0Cs&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3BnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=6e440f13\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pqzKQnmq0Cs</a><br />\n雖然係大紀元, 但可以聽吓教授講, 覺得有道理的話, 等美國之類外國勢力出咗招先再勇武都唔遲; <br />\n如果覺得冇道理或有咩陰謀, 可以繼續勇武繼續衝, 可能從中啲狗會提供更多核彈, 祇係核彈通常來自於手足嘅犧牲, 所以好似冇咁抵...<br />\n<br />\n勇武手足俾我感覺好多都係學生, 咪用呢幾日挑逗下啲狗仔狗女, 過下校園生活儲吓氣先再嚟過囉, 總之唔好好似以前D廢中淨係掛住讀書打波打J就得. 只要記得長時間mon住連登, 唔好俾個心冷卻, 一有需要就一齊再行出來好冇?"},{"pid":"47e32f833719a03f9a980bcdc30e9e020db279e4","tid":1537100,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:51:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MKrrRfp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMKrrRfp.jpg&h=a94ed6e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1e057a2f1012b1880783a9a8b5680ca3b67d05d","tid":1537100,"uid":268725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:52:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8B39Niu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8B39Niu.png&h=c9eeccd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e817590fc496b3ab7d297c0588f0a227ab367b","tid":153